description:
The mission for the MOON have halted, need to send in 47 spesialists. Take the core of the MOON or go home, we have the Buddies for the job. The Lunar Buddies - Expendables are suited up and ready to do what is necessary.

5 different suit badges with the expendables logo at only 10 % rarity,
6 different backgrounds, with stardust background at only 6 % rarity,
4 different logos on helmet, with shimmer at only 5% rarity
name: IOTA Lunar Buddies - Expendables  Third Wave
